snippet.title: Stellar Blade - The Journey: Part 2 (Behind The Scenes) | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/stellar-blade/

Step into the second part of our exclusive behind-the-scenes series! We’re we delve deeper into the making of Stellar Blade™ with the team at SHIFT UP.

Reclaim Earth for Humankind in Stellar Blade™, launching April 26, 2024 only on PS5® console.
Pre-order now for in-game bonuses.

#ps5games #ps5 #stellarblade 

Rated Mature
